                    In-Flight Roaming
                </div>
                <p>Warid International roaming joins hands with Aero Mobile & OnAir to help you scour the skies in any airline of your choice* whether you fly coach or executive, you are covered!This innovative in-flight roaming service is available for our postpaid subscribers. In-flight roaming will not only allow you to make & receive phone calls but you can also establish a two way text communication and let your friends and family know exactly where you are.</p>
                <h2>How to activate</h2>
                <p>For Aero Mobile enjoy in-flight roaming service on the following airlines and routes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Emirates B777 &amp; A330&nbsp;Flying to  Karachi
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Emirates B777&nbsp;Flying to  Lahore
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Emirates B777 &amp; A330&nbsp;Flying to  Islamabad
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Emirates A330&nbsp;Flying to  Peshawar
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>For <strong>OnAIR</strong> enjoy in-flight roaming service  on the following airlines and routes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Qatar Airways<br />
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>Currently onboard two Airbuses A320 aircraft - operating routes between Qatar  and to/from Europe, Middle East and Pakistan</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Ryanair
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>Currently Boeing 737  aircraft deployed - operating routes to/from various European and North African  cities.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Wataniya Airways
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>Currently three  Airbus A320 aircraft deployed - operating routes to/from Kuwait City and  between Dubai, Amman, Damascus, Sharm El Sheikh, Cairo, Beirut and Bahrain.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Royal Jordanian Airlines
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    Currently two Airbus A319  aircraft deployed - operating routes between Jordan and to/from Europe, Middle  East, North Africa and India.<br />
                    *Currently Only  Emirates flights are equipped with the Aero Mobile communication system &amp;  currently Rynair, Wataniya Airways &amp; Royal Jordanian airlines are equipped  with OnAir in-flight services.<br />
                    For Warid Press  release on the first in-flight roaming launch please click&nbsp;<u><a href="http://www.aeromobile.net/" target="_blank">AeroMobile</a></u>
                </p>
